                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-442" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES BAKER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a police inspector. On the 7th of May, at half-past seven o'clock in the morning, the prisoner came and gave himself up—he said he was the person that ran away with the £10 note.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183906170054"></xptr>
